        <ul class="comment-sublist">
            <li class="comment-wrapper">
                <article class="comment">
                    <div class="comment__date">28. 7. 2021</div>
                    <div class="comment__name">Franta</div>
                    <div class="comment__body">
                        <p>Donec suscipit rhoncus nulla, sed sodales arcu tristique quis. Nullam sed imperdiet neque. Curabitur iaculis magna quis odio gravida, ornare commodo odio aliquam.</p>
